CREATE TABLE movie_cast (movie_id INT, actor_id INT, character_name VARCHAR, PRIMARY KEY (movie_id, actor_id));</t><stat>select title, genre, first_name, last_name, character_name from movies inner join movie_cast on movies.movie_id = movie_cast.movie_id inner join actors on actors.actor_id = movie_cast.actor_id inner join directors on directors.director_id = movies.director_id;</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE actors (actor_id INT PRIMARY KEY, first_name VARCHAR, last_name VARCHAR, dob DATE, gender VARCHAR);
